      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mb-5 mt-32 rounded-2xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200">
        Lovosis Technology LLC, Dubai, is the authorized distributor of UNV
        Smart Interactive Panels
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl dark:text-gray-200">
      <strong>UNV Smart Interactive Panels</strong> are designed to transform the
      way you teach, learn, and collaborate. With advanced features like ultra-responsive
